---
title: Order Placement – Target Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor cust as Customer
    participant web as Web Portal
    participant orch as Order Orchestrator
    participant inv as Inventory API
    participant db as GCDB
    cust<<->>web: browse
    web--)orch: place order
    orch->>inv: reserve stock
    inv--)db: write reservation
    db-->>inv: ok
    Note over orch: Confirmation emitted asynchronously
